The paper focuses on image classification, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new method for image classification that is codebook-free, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of support vector machines (SVMs) for classification, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
